'''印度三虎棋'''（Pulijudam），是流傳於[[印度|印度]]的[[老虎棋|老虎棋]]類，與[[南印度三虎棋|南印度三虎棋]]相近<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hem.passagen.se/melki9/asian.htm |title=Asian Leopard Games (regional variants) |accessdate=2011-11-16 |archive-date=2011-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111112112945/http://hem.passagen.se/melki9/asian.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://plus.maths.org.uk/issue2/games/index.html |title=Maths.org.uk Game Description |access-date=2011-11-16 |archive-date=2008-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080612043845/http://plus.maths.org.uk/issue2/games/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

